Strategy_resp: I imagined myself in a restaurant, a typical local family owned Italian place to be specific. I envisioned what was around me and typed it out.

I thought of different people I know and what they do for a living. I thought of the services I need in day to day life, for example I had a mobile vet come to see my dogs last week. Things like that.

I looked around my room at items, and from those items determined if they began with the letter f or had a function related to the letter f. I also just thought of things I had encountered with the letter f and tried to recall them.
Much the same as before, I looked around the room at items for inspiration. I also thought about different things that began with S and noted them.
I thought of my experience working in a garage, what is in my home garage, and the properties of a typical garage.
I thought about the different sports available when I was in highschool. I also thought of sports friends were/are into, and sporting like the Olympics.
I thought of events in my life, the animals I've seen, specifically in those events.
I just let words come to me while focusing on the letter a. I thought about words I learned, words I use, whatever popped into my mind.
